      <title>智利反犯罪策划者因强奸指控辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chile-anti-crime-mastermind-steps-down-following-rape-allegation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利内政部副部长曼努埃尔·蒙萨尔维 (Manuel Monsalve) 因涉嫌强奸而接受调查的报道发布后辞职，这一令人震惊的进展导致政府失去了一位顶级打击犯罪的官员。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/chile-anti-crime-mastermind-steps-down-following-rape-allegation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:20:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>四位部长计划离职，特鲁多将改组内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/trudeau-to-shuffle-cabinet-as-four-ministers-plan-departures</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于一些部长决定不参加下次选举，加拿大总理贾斯汀·特鲁多将在未来几周内改组内阁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/trudeau-to-shuffle-cabinet-as-four-ministers-plan-departures</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 18:00:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加纳反对党议员空出席位，目前占据议会多数席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ghana-opposition-now-majority-in-parliament-as-mps-vacate-seats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加纳反对党全国民主大会在议长宣布四名议员因叛逃而出现议席空缺后，获得了议会多数席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/ghana-opposition-now-majority-in-parliament-as-mps-vacate-seats</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 17:51:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国国家财富基金宣布拨款 10 亿英镑用于住宅改造</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/uk-national-wealth-fund-announces-1-billion-for-home-retrofits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国国家财富基金、巴克莱银行和劳埃德银行集团宣布提供10亿英镑贷款，资助低收入住房的隔热和低碳供暖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/uk-national-wealth-fund-announces-1-billion-for-home-retrofits</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 17:17:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
